Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:08.61,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Shiragami...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:10.53,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.40,jitsuwa-flashback,Youko,0,0,0,,Kuromine-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:17.85,jitsuwa-flashback,Asahi,0,0,0,,Shiragami!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:23.03,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prečo si takto odišla?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:24.83,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Upokoj sa, Kuromine Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:26.76,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Predsedníčka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:29.92,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Aizawa, mne nikto poriadne nič nepovedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:32.42,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Je pravda, že bola unesená?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:35.05,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Hej, obrovským netopierom, akého som ešte nikdy predtým nevidela.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:38.00,jitsuwa-main,Shiho,0,0,0,,Obrovský netopier, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:40.89,jitsuwa-main,Shiho,0,0,0,,Tak to musel byť niekto z jej rodiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:43.89,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prosím, ponáhľajte sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:45.52,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Ešte stále som tvoja učiteľka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.52,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Už som na rýchlostnom limite.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.40,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Okrem toho som sa musela vzdať
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:51.36,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,môjho piva pred jedlom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:52.63,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,piva po jedle,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:53.97,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,piva pred spaním,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.27,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,môjho víkendového piva
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:57.36,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,a všetkých ostatných druhov pív,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.74,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,aby som si mohla dovoliť toto nové auto!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:04.25,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Myslím, že táto veta prezradila všetko o vašom súkromnom živote.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.47,0:01:06.71,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,Ty si taká stará dievka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:10.59,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,Kúpiš si nové auto, keď nemáš ani chlapa, ktorý by v ňom vedľa teba sedel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:11.46,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Kedy si...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:13.16,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,Pokoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:16.06,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,S mojimi diabolskými schopnosťami
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:18.64,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,tam môžeme byť do zotmenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:19.84,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:20.68,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,P-Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:22.81,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,Choď spať, stará dievka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:25.98,jitsuwa-main,All,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.31,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,Dobre sa držte!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:46.95,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Titulky od GAW-Subs\Nwww.gawsubs.com
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:12.96,jitsuwa-ep-title,Text,0,0,0,,Poďme spolu\Ndomov!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:12.22,jitsuwa-main,Text,0,0,0,,Poďme spolu domov!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.40,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Prečo by ste sa mali ospravedlňovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:21.18,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Len som vám položila otázku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:24.89,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Kde je moje nové auto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:27.61,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,K-Koumoto-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.61,0:03:29.43,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Um, tamto je.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:32.04,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Huh? O čom to hovoríte?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.64,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,To je len hromada šrotu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.89,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,Počuj, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:40.78,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,Dodržala som svoj sľub Kurominemu, že sa sem dnes večer dostaneme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:44.78,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,A diabol si vždy pýta cenu za každý sľub.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:47.51,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,No a čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.55,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,Chcem tým povedať,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.21,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,tvoje nové auto bola tá cena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.12,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Dopekla s tebou, ty stará rašpľa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.88,jitsuwa-main,Akane,0,0,0,,Ja sa postarám o tú starú dievku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:02.22,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Kuromine Asahi. Shishido Shiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.26,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ste pripravení?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:07.02,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Počkaj, predsedníčka, si do toho príliš zabratá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.35,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Nie, nie som.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.52,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Chceme infiltrovať vilu upíra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:13.69,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Musíme byť pripravení.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:16.72,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Kuromine Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:21.01,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Než túto operáciu začneme, musím sa ti za niečo ospravedlniť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.70,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Moje sebecké správanie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:27.22,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,ti zase spôsobilo problémy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.12,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Naozaj mi je to ľúto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.87,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Počkaj, predsedníčka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.80,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ako odčinenie žiadam,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:37.08,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,aby si mi dovolil sa čo najviac snažiť pri záchrane Shiragami Youko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:40.21,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Tým sa netráp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:43.97,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To celé ma prekvapilo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:47.89,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,ale naozaj by sa nám tvoja pomoc hodila.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.27,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,S-Správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:54.92,jitsuwa-main,Shiho,0,0,0,,Vy dvaja ste zase do seba buchnutí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.48,jitsuwa-main,All,0,0,0,,N-Nie sme!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:57.88,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.48,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Kuromine a Shishido,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.96,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,týmto začíname operácie "záchrana Shiragami Youko".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.33,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Áno, kapitánka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.75,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to tak, že sa tadiaľto dostaneme dnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:14.88,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Poďme.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.40,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Čo je to za miesto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.24,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Buďte opatrní.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.14,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Čo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:55.50,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Kto sa neohlásene vkradol do môjho domu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.66,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Je obrovský!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:58.00,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,K-Kto ste?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.29,jitsuwa-main,Shiho,0,0,0,,Oh, zabudla som vám povedať.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.40,jitsuwa-main,Shiho,0,0,0,,Toto je Youkin otec.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.26,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:07.79,jitsuwa-internal,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Už len pomyslieť si, že takýto obrovský tvor existuje na tejto planéte!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.93,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Vôbec sa nepodobá na Shiragami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.89,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Čo sú to za ľudia, Shiho?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.61,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,R-Radi vás spoznávame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.90,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Som spolužiak Shiragami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.27,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Volám sa Kuromine Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.22,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prišiel som vás požiadať o láskavosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.64,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:27.24,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prosím, vráťte nám Shiragami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:28.61,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:32.37,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Čo je to za blbosť, chlapče?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.94,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Aký máš vzťah s mojou dcérou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.12,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Oci?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.62,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Tu si.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.20,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Sh-Shiragami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.67,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Huh? Kuromine-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:45.46,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Čo tu... Aj vy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:46.92,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Uhni, Youko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.73,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Nepleť sa do toho, hlupaňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:49.88,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.30,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Čo myslíš tou hlupaňou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.18,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Pretože to aj si!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:55.60,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Čo to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.89,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to tak, že ten cesnakový prášok zaberá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:03.04,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Rýchlo! Ber Shiragami Youko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:04.23,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.69,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Utekajme, Shiragami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.57,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Č-Čo sa to deje, Kuromine-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:12.11,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Berieme ťa späť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.06,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Hej, ale prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.62,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Týka sa to tvojho tajomstva.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.88,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,P-Počkaj chvíľu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.62,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Myslím, že si niečo zle pochopil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.63,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Dozvedela som sa, že moja mama leží chorá v posteli,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.38,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,tak som sa len prišla o ňu postarať.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.38,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Čože? Ty sa staráš o...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.64,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,... tvoju chorú mamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:36.88,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Takže všetko, čo sme doteraz urobili...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.63,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,... bolo len veľké nedorozumenie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.52,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Tak to je.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:45.59,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Kto by zle pochopil toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:51.28,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Po tom, čo si povedala niečo sugestívne, ako: \N"Poď po škole na strechu..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.68,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Uh... Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.66,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Len som ti chcela povedať, že idem na čas domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.38,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,O-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:03.50,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Úplne som si myslel, že sa tvoj otec dozvedel o tvojom tajomstve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.00,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Chlapče...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.16,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Čo si to práve povedal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.94,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Ty poznáš
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.43,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Youkine tajomstvo, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.01,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nie, nie, nepoznám!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.85,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Museli ste ma zle rozumieť!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:21.36,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Tak načo bol potom ten cesnak?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:26.98,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,P-Potrebujem ho dnes na večeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.52,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.94,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,N-Na—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:32.70,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Naozaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:35.28,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Tvoja tvár hovorí, že klameš!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.14,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Youko, sľúbila si to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:41.67,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Keďže je tvoje tajomstvo vonku, tvoj školský život
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.46,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,práve skončil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.08,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Teraz máme šancu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.50,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ber to a utekaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:48.88,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Jasné!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.42,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Poďme, Shiragami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.14,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.88,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Ty malý...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:52.88,jitsuwa-overlap,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.68,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Pri všetkej úcte, vypočujte si ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:09:00.35,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Kuromine Asahi nie je ten typ muža, za ktorého—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.32,jitsuwa-main,Shiho,0,0,0,,Už odišiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:03.98,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:08.27,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Neujdeš mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:09.68,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Niečo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:11.28,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nie je tam niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:12.57,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Tu je to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.07,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Kríž nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.99,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.83,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Chceš sa so mnou biť?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.49,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Teraz je naozaj naštvaný!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.37,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nemáme tam nič iné?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.70,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Oh! To...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.67,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To snáď nie, predsedníčka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.38,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Zabralo to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.30,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Kuromine-kun, sem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:40.97,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Au...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.52,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,K-Kde to sme?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.18,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Toto je moja izba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:47.10,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Tvoja izba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:48.33,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:52.62,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Môj otec ako upír nemá dovolené vojsť do mojej izby bez dovolenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:53.82,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Nateraz sme v bezpečí.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.67,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Takto to funguje?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.32,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,T-To bokom...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:01.35,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prepáč, Shiragami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:02.83,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,K-Kuromine-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.96,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Je to moja vina, že tvoj otec vie o tom, že je tvoje tajomstvo vyzradené.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:10.33,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Počuj... ako som už povedala,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:15.26,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,nie je to tvoja vina, že je moje tajomstvo vonku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:16.58,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,V prvom rade je to moja vina, 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:20.21,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,že som nedokázala dodržať sľub, ktorý som dala otcovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:24.78,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Takže sa nemusíš tak snažiť, aby si so mnou ušiel a podobne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:26.73,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,A-Ale, Shiragami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:30.17,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,A chcem sa aj ospravedlniť.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:34.82,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Úprimne, je tu ešte niečo, čo som ti chcela
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.74,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,povedať na streche.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:39.36,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Sama tomu veľmi nerozumiem,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.24,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,ale v poslednej dobe, keď ťa vidím, z nejakého dôvodu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:45.30,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,som sa cítila divne a nakoniec som sa ti začala vyhýbať.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.83,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Naozaj ma to mrzí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.37,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Prepáč, Kuromine-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.89,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nemusíš sa ospravedlňovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.07,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,O-Oh, hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:56.76,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Aj ja som ti chcel niečo povedať.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:59.22,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ohľadom toho festivalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:08.10,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Len som pomohol predsedníčke, keď spadla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.44,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Aj to, čo sa stalo v škole, bola len nehoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.86,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nie je to tak, ako si myslíš!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:16.28,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Takže nechcem, aby si to zle pochopila...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:19.96,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Čo to vlastne v takúto chvíľu hovorím?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:23.23,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To som tým nemyslel... Ja, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:24.69,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Každopádne, prepáč!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:27.96,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Ty si vždy taký, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.92,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Naozaj si otvorená kniha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.64,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Shiragami...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.00,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Tak—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:40.47,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Si tam vnútri, však, Youko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.49,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Oci?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.76,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Našiel nás!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.97,jitsuwa-overlap,Dad,0,0,0,,Otvor, sopliak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.97,bubbles,Okada,0,0,0,,{\an7}Dajme tomu                                 Začínam byť nervózny.                          Asi sme na rade!\Núžasný záver!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:53.69,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Si tam, však, Youko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.71,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Počkaj, oci, čo to robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.39,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Myslel som, že nemôže ísť dnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:58.30,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Ten hlas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.19,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,To je ten chalan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:04.17,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Máš odvahu vojsť do izby mojej dcéry, chlapče!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.06,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Ty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:08.18,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Čo chceš robiť s Youko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.68,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ja nič nerobím!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.46,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Okamžite poď sem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.92,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,T-To naozaj nemôžem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:17.29,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Tak ťa vytiahnem von!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.76,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Nerob nič šialené, otec!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.27,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Roztrhám tú bariéru na kusy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.49,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Genjirou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.65,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Čo to tam robíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.60,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,T-Touko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.72,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.92,jitsuwa-main,Shiho,0,0,0,,Priviedla som ju sem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.53,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Naháňaš tu Youkiných spolužiakov
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.70,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,a nakoniec si zdemoloval dom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.13,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,N-Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.20,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Povedal, že pozná Youkino tajomstvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:48.81,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:53.33,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Tak sa asi budeme musieť trochu porozprávať.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.83,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Počkaj! Čo chceš robiť s tými vecami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.67,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,D-Dobre, Touko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:00.67,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Chápem to! Tak, prosím, všetko, len to nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.67,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Nie kôl do môjho srdca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:05.51,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:09.42,jitsuwa-main,Shiho,0,0,0,,Dobre, vy dvaja, bavte sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.08,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.36,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Myslel som si, že tvoja mama je chorá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.27,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Nuž, vlastne,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.86,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,je pravda, že mama ochorela a mala horúčku,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:21.44,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,ale otec prehnane reagoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:23.44,jitsuwa-flashback,Dad,0,0,0,,Youko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:24.78,jitsuwa-flashback,Dad,0,0,0,,Rýchlo poď domov!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.26,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Naozaj to nebolo nič vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.12,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Tak čo to bolo za netopiera?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.99,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,To ma môj otec prišiel v panike vyzdvihnúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:34.13,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Vystresuje sa kvôli ničomu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:38.80,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,M-Môj dojem z tvojho otca sa práve otočil o 180 stupňov.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:41.89,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:44.10,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Chvíľu tu budeme v bezpečí.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:46.71,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ale ako dlho tu budeme musieť ostať?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.60,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Nuž...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:52.14,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Som si istá, že to otec ráno vzdá a pôjde spať.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.80,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,R-Ráno?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:55.56,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.67,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,To nie...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:04.94,jitsuwa-internal,Asahi,0,0,0,,Len my dvaja v Shiragaminej izbe do rána?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:08.41,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Veľmi sa neobzeraj!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:12.20,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Pozor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.38,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ste vy dvaja... v poriadku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:23.35,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,A-Aizawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.96,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,P-Predsedníčka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:33.14,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Čo to robíš, Eromine Asahi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:34.81,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Neuhýbaj sa mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.85,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Whoa! Nie kladivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.35,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,To nie je kladivo! To je prístroj na vymazávanie spomienok!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.23,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To je ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.48,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To je ono, predsedníčka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:46.49,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Sakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.99,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Prečo sa vždy nakričí iba na mňa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.74,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Idem dnu, oci.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:58.00,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Kuromine-kun chce s tebou hovoriť.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.71,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Chlapče, čo chceš?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:01.94,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Nuž...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.71,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prišiel som vás požiadať o láskavosť, otec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.90,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Povedal si "otec"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:09.18,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Nemáš právo mi tak hovoriť!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:09.86,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Počkať...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:13.26,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,N-Nechceš ma požiadať o Youkinu ruku, však?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.26,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.72,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,S-Samozrejme, že nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:16.89,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,My spolu ani len nerandíme!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:18.68,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Randenie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.80,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Teraz to schytáš, chlapče.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:23.81,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,P-Povedal som, že nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:26.26,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Oci, niečím takým sa vôbec nemusíš trápiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:29.32,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,O teba sa nebojím!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:32.08,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Oh, hej, predsedníčka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.92,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Máš to kladivo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:34.82,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:36.28,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Otec,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:39.58,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,rana do hlavy týmto kladivom dokáže vymazať spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.74,0:15:40.75,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.46,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Čo je to za nápad, Kuromine Asahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:46.21,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Nemôžem pozemšťanovi dovoliť, aby to použil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:48.42,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Čo to robíš, predsedníčka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.14,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Čo je to, dopekla?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.01,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.32,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,T-To nie... Je to len... Nie je!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.79,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Oh, hej! Oci, veď si predsa upír!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.96,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,O-Oh, správne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:01.93,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Je v poriadku, ak bude vedieť, že si mimozemšťan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:03.77,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Daj to sem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:08.65,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Dobre, povedzme, že naozaj môžeš tým kladivom vymazať spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.54,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,A čo s tým?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.96,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Chcem od vás sľub.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:14.77,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Hovoríš sľub?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:15.53,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:19.95,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prosím, sľúbte mi, že ak si zmažem všetky spomienky na Shiragamino tajomstvo,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:23.25,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Shiragami nebude musieť odísť zo školy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:27.13,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Shiragami má veľa priateľov.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.45,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Vymažte mi spomienky
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:33.05,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,a Shiragami sa bude môcť vrátiť k šťastnému školskému životu, ktorý doteraz viedla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.30,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prosím, otec.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:36.74,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Aj ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.83,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,som Shiragamin kamarát.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.69,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Aj keď stratím spomienky,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.75,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,chcem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:48.02,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,stále chrániť Youko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.37,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Dobre teda, chlapče.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:01.53,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Takže...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:04.68,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Ale to mi nestačí.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:09.21,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Zmaž si všetky spomienky na Youko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:13.17,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Ak si pripravený to urobiť, súhlasím s tým sľubom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.12,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Oci, čo to—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.18,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ak to urobím...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:19.84,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Shiragami sa môže vrátiť do školy, správne?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:24.49,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Shiragami Genjirou vždy dodrží svoje slovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:28.15,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Predsedníčka, smiem prosiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:34.08,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,N-Nuž, je možné, ak udriem dosť silno...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.14,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Prosím, najtvrdšie, ako vieš.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.09,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Si si istý?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:41.65,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:58.71,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Nemôžem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:03.60,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Nedokážem to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.40,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Vďaka, predsedníčka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:12.38,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Urobím to sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.63,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:33.38,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Shiragami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:35.17,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Kuromine-kun, ty hlupák!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:37.28,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Už som ti povedala!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.70,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Nemusíš takto trpieť, aby si ochránil moje tajomstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:45.22,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Nechcem, aby si zachádzal takto ďaleko len kvôli môjmu tajomstvu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.74,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Aizawa-san, Akemi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.41,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Oka-kun a ostatní chalani
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:51.62,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,a Shiho, ktorá práve prestúpila...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:55.84,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,To vďaka tebe som sa s nimi všetkými spriatelila.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:19:00.64,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Aj keby si na mňa zabudol len kvôli uchovaniu môjho tajomstva,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.49,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,ja stále mám svoje spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:06.82,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Ako môže byť škola pre mňa potom zábavná?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:09.00,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Pretože, Asahi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:11.75,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,si môj vzácny...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:13.76,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Môj vzácny...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:20.97,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.40,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Oci?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.22,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.87,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Čo sa práve...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.31,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,T-To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:31.90,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,N-Nemožné!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:34.23,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Zbraň na vymazávanie spomienok
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:38.69,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,náhodou zasiahla tvojho otca a zmazala mu spomienky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.76,jitsuwa-main,All,0,0,0,,Č-Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.32,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Prepáčte.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.00,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Stihla som spraviť len toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:49.31,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,To nevadí. Ďakujeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.83,jitsuwa-main,Shiho,0,0,0,,Dobrú chuť.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.84,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Chceš ryžové guličky, Aizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:58.25,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:02.56,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Prepáč mi to všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:04.50,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Čo také.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.51,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Oh, to nie je ohľadom teba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:10.03,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Ale pomyslieť si, že si mala rovnaké city ako ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:12.80,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Čo si povedala predtým.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.80,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Som rada s vami...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.78,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,So všetkými.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:20.51,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Aj ty, hej?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:21.82,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,To som rada.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.40,jitsuwa-internal,Nagisa,0,0,0,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:28.26,jitsuwa-internal,,0,0,0,,myslím, že to nie je jediná vec, čo cítime rovnako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.84,0:20:31.24,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Shiragami Youko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:36.23,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,Ak si jedného dňa uvedomíš niečo ohľadom seba,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.43,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,mnou sa netráp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.84,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Niečo ohľadom seba?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.28,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,O čom to hovoríš, Aizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:47.20,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,To je jedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:50.81,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Naozaj mi je to ľúto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:54.76,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Moji študenti vám asi spôsobili veľa problémov.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:57.40,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Nie, nie, tým sa netrápte.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.44,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Sensei, čo sa stalo s autom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:03.48,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Opravila ho svojimi diabolskými schopnosťami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:06.66,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Nie, dala som jej to v plnej výške zaplatiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.62,jitsuwa-main,Sensei,0,0,0,,Pôjdeme už.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.59,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Ďakujeme za všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:12.64,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Prosím, príďte nás všetci niekedy navštíviť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:13.43,jitsuwa-main,All,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:14.41,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Maj sa, mami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:18.42,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Nemáš s tým problém, drahý?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.71,jitsuwa-main,Mom,0,0,0,,Youko odchádza.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.28,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Tá sprostá sopľaňa ma nezaujíma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:28.55,jitsuwa-main,Dad,0,0,0,,Kto jej sem vlastne kázal prísť?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.67,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Zabudni na to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:38.32,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Som zvedavý, či tvoj otec naozaj stratil spomienky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:41.41,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Myslím, že bude v poriadku, vzhľadom na to, ako sa teraz správa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:45.24,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,H-Huh? Tvoj otec...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.11,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Oci?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:49.24,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Nevrátili sa mu spomienky, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.69,jitsuwa-main,Shiho,0,0,0,,Možno sa snaží dohnať auto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:52.87,jitsuwa-main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Isto nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.17,0:21:55.37,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Počkať, on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:58.37,jitsuwa-main,,0,0,0,,kýva na teba, Shiragami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:02.00,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,T-Teda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.79,0:22:03.98,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Je taký...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.73,0:22:07.01,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Oci!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:09.53,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:11.93,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Čoskoro sa vidíme!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:25.50,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Tvoj otec je dobrý človek.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:27.01,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:29.83,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Hej, Shiragami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:35.36,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Keď si ma včera oslovila prvým menom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:37.87,jitsuwa-main,Asahi,0,0,0,,Čo si mi chcela povedať?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:40.96,jitsuwa-flashback,Youko,0,0,0,,Pretože, Asahi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:42.96,jitsuwa-flashback,,0,0,0,,si môj vzácny...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:45.84,jitsuwa-main,Youko,0,0,0,,Nič, Kuromine-kun.
